name: Anatolia X Nike Air Force 1
description:
The name Anatolia comes from the Greek Aνατολή (Αnatolí), and means "the place of the rising sun." 

Throughout history we can see that Anatolia played a big role in our common global history. 

Anatolia is the “bridge” between east and west and it still holds some global cultural monuments and values like Hagia Sophia, Gobekli Tepe and Rumi

As Hagia, we have transformed a 20th century monument with Anatolian understanding and aesthetics.

When our limit of sales are met, Hagia will start producing Anatolian Nike Air Force 1’s and send them to one of our collectors.

You can see the shoe in our social media accounts

More Air Force 1’s will come ! 


Enjoy !
